      {
        "level": 0,
        "text": "Harris Corner Detector"
      }
    ],
    "has_images": false,
    "image_files": []
  },
  {
    "slide": 2,
    "title": "",
    "texts": [
      {
        "level": 0,
        "text": "Motivation: Matching Problem"
      },
      {
        "level": 0,
        "text": "Vision tasks such as stereo and motion estimation require  finding corresponding features across two or more views."
      }
    ],
    "has_images": false,
    "image_files": []
  },
  {
    "slide": 3,
    "title": "",
    "texts": [
      {
        "level": 0,
        "text": "Motivation: Patch Matching"
      },
      {
        "level": 0,
        "text": "Task: find the best (most similar) patch in a second image"
      },
      {
        "level": 0,
        "text": "?"
      },
      {
        "level": 0,
        "text": "="
      },
      {
        "level": 0,
        "text": "Elements to be matched are image patches of fixed size"
      }
    ],
    "has_images": false,
    "image_files": []
  },
  {
    "slide": 4,
    "title": "",
    "texts": [
      {
        "level": 0,
        "text": "Not all Patches are Created Equal!"
      },
      {
        "level": 0,
        "text": "Intuition: this would be a good patch for matching, since  it is very distinctive (there is only one patch in the second  frame that looks similar)."
      },
      {
        "level": 0,
        "text": "?"
      },
      {
        "level": 0,
        "text": "="
      }
    ],
    "has_images": false,
    "image_files": []
  },
  {
    "slide": 5,
    "title": "",
    "texts": [
      {
        "level": 0,
        "text": "Not all Patches are Created Equal!"
      },
      {
        "level": 0,
        "text": "Intuition: this would be a BAD patch for matching, since  it is not very distinctive (there are many similar patches  in the second frame)"
      },
      {
        "level": 0,
        "text": "?"
      },
      {
        "level": 0,
        "text": "="
      }
    ],
    "has_images": false,
    "image_files": []
  },
  {
    "slide": 6,
    "title": "",
    "texts": [
      {
        "level": 0,
        "text": "What are Corners?"
      },
      {
        "level": 0,
        "text": "They are good features to match!"
      }
    ],
    "has_images": true,
    "image_files": [
      "/home/rishabh/Documents/IITM/CV/Notes/MD/Images/extracted/Harris Corner Detector/slide_06_img_1.jpg"
    ]
  },
  {
    "slide": 7,
    "title": "",
    "texts": [
      {
        "level": 0,
        "text": "Corner Points: Basic Idea"
      },
      {
        "level": 0,
        "text": "We should easily recognize the point by looking  at intensity values within a small window"
      },
      {
        "level": 0,
        "text": "Shifting the window in any direction should yield  a large change in appearance."
      }
    ],
    "has_images": true,
    "image_files": [
      "/home/rishabh/Documents/IITM/CV/Notes/MD/Images/extracted/Harris Corner Detector/slide_07_img_1.png"
    ]
  },
  {
    "slide": 8,
    "title": "",
    "texts": [
      {
        "level": 0,
        "text": "Harris Corner Detector: Basic Idea"
      },
      {
        "level": 0,
        "text": "Harris corner detector gives a mathematical  approach for determining which case holds."
      }
    ],
    "has_images": true,
    "image_files": [
      "/home/rishabh/Documents/IITM/CV/Notes/MD/Images/extracted/Harris Corner Detector/slide_08_img_1.png",
